methods.name: void onOutgoingEmergencyCall(@NonNull EmergencyNumber placedEmergencyNumber, int subscriptionId)
methods.comment:
* Callback invoked when an outgoing call is placed to an emergency number. *

* This method will be called when an emergency call is placed on any subscription * (including the no-SIM case), regardless of which subscription this callback was * registered on. *

* * @param placedEmergencyNumber The {@link EmergencyNumber} the emergency call was * placed to. * @param subscriptionId The subscription ID used to place the emergency call. If the * emergency call was placed without a valid subscription * (e.g. when there are no SIM cards in the device), this * will be * equal to * {@link SubscriptionManager#INVALID_SUBSCRIPTION_ID}.

methodNames: void onOutgoingEmergencyCall(@NonNull EmergencyNumber placedEmergencyNumber, int subscriptionId)
